!item [Name:]
ØSet foreground colourÆ - Set foreground colour for text.

!item [Opcode:]
200 (Sub-Opcode 0)

!item [Syntax:]
int16_t vst_fg_color ( int16_t handle, int32_t color_space, COLOR_ENTRY *fg_color );

!item [Description:]
The call vst_fg_color sets the foreground colour for text.

!begin_xlist !short [color_space]
!item [Parameter]
Meaning
!item [~]
~
!item [handle]
Workstation identifier
!item [color_space]
Colour space (at present only 0 for the colour space set, or CSPACE_RGB)
!item [fg_color]
COLOR_ENTRY of the foreground colour
!end_xlist


!item [(!nolink [Return]) value:]
-1 = Wrong subfunction number (!nl)
~0 = Function not present (!nl)
~1 = All OK

!item [Availability:]
NVDI 5.00 onwards.

!item [Group:]
